00:00:15.078 --> 00:00:15.879 position:24% line:89% align:start
[clearing throat]

00:00:16.980 --> 00:00:18.815 position:5% line:65% align:start
Good evening, ladies
and gentlemen!

00:00:19.382 --> 00:00:23.120 position:5% line:77% align:start
What an incredibly special event
we have for you here in Bangkok
this evening,

00:00:23.154 --> 00:00:28.025 position:7% line:77% align:start
because tonight our exclusive
underground showcase is finally
reaching the end of its run.

00:00:29.127 --> 00:00:32.430 position:5% line:83% align:start
On this very day... in the year
twenty-six nineteen...

00:00:33.131 --> 00:00:35.534 position:10% line:83% align:start
the strongest man on earth-
Oh, I mean...

00:00:36.134 --> 00:00:39.838 position:10% line:77% align:start
The strongest man <i>under</i> the
earth shall be decided!
[chuckle]

00:00:46.279 --> 00:00:51.118 position:5% line:5% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>Am I dreaming? I've</i>
 <i>seen this kind of thing a</i>
 <i>hundred times in comic books... </i>

00:00:52.585 --> 00:00:56.790 position:7% line:5% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Yeah, it does seem </i>
 <i>like fiction. But...</i>

00:00:57.591 --> 00:01:04.799 position:7% line:5% align:start
 <i>The world has no shortage of </i>
 <i>CEOs and oil tycoons,  who </i>
 <i>make millions, or billions, a</i>
 <i>month. </i>

00:01:05.599 --> 00:01:10.805 position:13% line:5% align:start
 <i>But the people here are a </i>
 <i>special kind of rich that puts</i>
 <i>normal wealth to shame. </i>

00:01:11.473 --> 00:01:14.476 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>When they get together... their</i>
 <i>minds warp. </i>

00:01:15.477 --> 00:01:19.315 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>They become consumed with lust </i>
 <i>for the theater of murder.</i>

00:01:20.149 --> 00:01:22.485 position:13% line:5% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>So...he's still</i>
 <i>alive then?</i>

00:01:23.619 --> 00:01:25.322 position:27% line:5% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Yeah.</i>

00:01:27.658 --> 00:01:29.826 position:24% line:89% align:start
[Crowd murmuring]

00:01:31.194 --> 00:01:34.198 position:7% line:83% align:start
Up first, standing in the blue
corner, we have...

00:01:36.134 --> 00:01:37.001 position:16% line:89% align:start
[uncomfortable chuckle]

00:01:38.970 --> 00:01:42.540 position:16% line:77% align:start
...the twenty-something
supernova with a secret and
shady past.

00:01:43.074 --> 00:01:45.177 position:33% line:89% align:start
Hi-za-ma-ru!

00:01:45.543 --> 00:01:47.913 position:27% line:89% align:start
Akari Hizamaru!

00:01:47.947 --> 00:01:49.348 position:27% line:89% align:start
[Crowd cheering]

00:01:51.917 --> 00:01:56.356 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>One hundred and seventy-seven </i>
 <i>centimeters tall and weighing in</i>
 <i>at ninety-one kilograms, he's a</i>
 <i>karate master from Japan!  </i>

00:02:00.360 --> 00:02:01.561 position:13% line:5% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>So that's him.</i>

00:02:02.562 --> 00:02:07.534 position:33% line:5% align:start
01  SYMPTOM

00:02:32.695 --> 00:02:38.435 position:5% line:77% align:start
(EMCEE) <i>It's such a sad story...</i>
 <i>Akari's childhood sweetheart,</i>
 <i>who's an orphan just like him,</i>

00:02:38.469 --> 00:02:42.673 position:13% line:77% align:start
 <i>is suffering from a malady</i>
 <i>that's left doctors completely</i>
 <i>baffled.  </i>

00:02:43.240 --> 00:02:45.542 position:5% line:5% align:start
 <i>Does he have to say that every </i>
 <i>time?</i>

00:02:45.576 --> 00:02:48.046 position:13% line:83% align:start
Her only hope is an organ
transplant!

00:02:48.512 --> 00:02:49.646 position:21% line:89% align:start
Poor Akari, here...

00:02:51.616 --> 00:02:55.086 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>...is after the prize money </i>
 <i>because he's desperate to help</i>
 <i>out his dear old friend!</i>

00:02:55.720 --> 00:02:56.921 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yeah!

00:02:57.922 --> 00:03:00.525 position:5% line:83% align:start
That's right! You got that, you
rich bastards?!

00:03:00.558 --> 00:03:03.963 position:5% line:77% align:start
(OIL BARON) <i>Impressive! And for</i>
 <i>some bitch you haven't even</i>
 <i>screwed!</i>

00:03:04.597 --> 00:03:08.368 position:5% line:77% align:start
(EMCEE) <i>But the final opponent </i>
 <i>he's facing is exceptionally</i>
 <i>fierce.</i>

00:03:08.634 --> 00:03:11.438 position:10% line:89% align:start
 <i>He is, our undefeated king!</i>

00:03:13.740 --> 00:03:20.081 position:7% line:71% align:start
 <i>Brian Chaomy, fourteen years </i>
 <i>old, two hundred fifty-one</i>
 <i>centimeters tall, three hundred</i>
 <i>forty-two kilograms! </i>

00:03:20.114 --> 00:03:23.651 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>An American with, shall we say,</i>
 <i>his own martial arts style... </i>

00:03:24.052 --> 00:03:27.389 position:10% line:83% align:start
He's simply, a natural-born
killer!

00:03:29.791 --> 00:03:35.230 position:7% line:89% align:start
[growling, snarling, roaring]

00:03:35.465 --> 00:03:36.399 position:5% line:5% align:start
(AKARI) <i>What the-?!</i>

00:03:36.433 --> 00:03:38.767 position:35% line:89% align:start
[snarling]

00:03:38.801 --> 00:03:40.036 position:41% line:89% align:start
[roar]

00:03:40.070 --> 00:03:41.037 position:38% line:89% align:start
[strike]

00:03:41.071 --> 00:03:44.607 position:7% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) [struggling, unsteady]

00:03:44.641 --> 00:03:49.346 position:7% line:77% align:start
(EMCEE) <i>Brian's an omnivore by</i>
 <i>nature, but we've been feeding</i>
 <i>him human flesh. </i>

00:03:49.380 --> 00:03:51.515 position:19% line:5% align:start
 <i>Those pieces of shit!</i>

00:03:51.781 --> 00:03:53.984 position:16% line:5% align:start
 <i>They're not giving me a</i>
 <i>chance!  </i>

00:03:54.385 --> 00:03:54.985 position:38% line:5% align:start
 <i>Damnit!</i>

00:04:01.725 --> 00:04:06.164 position:19% line:89% align:start
Yuriko! Just hang on!

00:04:06.198 --> 00:04:12.472 position:24% line:89% align:start
[crowd murmuring]

00:04:12.505 --> 00:04:14.173 position:24% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) [laughing]

00:04:14.207 --> 00:04:16.342 position:30% line:89% align:start
Now listen up!

00:04:16.543 --> 00:04:21.381 position:5% line:77% align:start
Get ready! 'Cause this one-sided
story you've been watching ends
right now!

00:04:21.415 --> 00:04:26.854 position:27% line:89% align:start
[crowd cheering]

00:04:26.887 --> 00:04:28.789 position:35% line:89% align:start
[roaring]

00:04:28.822 --> 00:04:30.592 position:7% line:5% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Time to put this bear</i>
 <i>down!</i>

00:04:32.327 --> 00:04:34.129 position:35% line:89% align:start
[yelling]

00:04:34.162 --> 00:04:34.628 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:04:35.196 --> 00:04:39.568 position:19% line:89% align:start
[grunts and struggles]

00:04:39.602 --> 00:04:40.503 position:5% line:89% align:start
[groaning in pain]

00:04:41.604 --> 00:04:44.373 position:10% line:89% align:start
[thuds and groaning in pain]

00:04:46.308 --> 00:04:49.044 position:24% line:89% align:start
[heavy breathing]

00:04:49.879 --> 00:04:51.046 position:47% line:89% align:start
(BEAR) [growling]

00:04:51.481 --> 00:04:51.814 position:38% line:89% align:start
[smack]

00:04:52.382 --> 00:04:57.120 position:16% line:89% align:start
[thud and moans in pain]

00:04:57.154 --> 00:05:02.393 position:5% line:89% align:start
[moaning, struggling to breath]

00:05:02.426 --> 00:05:05.396 position:38% line:89% align:start
[snarl]

00:05:05.429 --> 00:05:11.335 position:13% line:89% align:start
[crunching and slobbering]

00:05:17.476 --> 00:05:20.613 position:5% line:5% align:start
(YURIKO) You know, too...You do,
don't you?

00:05:22.348 --> 00:05:23.650 position:19% line:89% align:start
[angry grunt] <i>Just go home!</i>

00:05:23.849 --> 00:05:26.252 position:10% line:83% align:start
Does watching me waste away
amuse you?!

00:05:26.653 --> 00:05:28.555 position:5% line:89% align:start
[hyperventilating] Is that why?!

00:05:29.255 --> 00:05:32.759 position:7% line:83% align:start
Is that why you come here to
visit me day after day?!

00:05:33.327 --> 00:05:35.095 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:05:35.429 --> 00:05:36.330 position:52% line:89% align:start
(YURIKO) <i>You...</i>

00:05:36.363 --> 00:05:37.531 position:13% line:5% align:start
Who do you think you are?!

00:05:38.566 --> 00:05:40.100 position:19% line:5% align:start
You're just a monster!

00:05:40.602 --> 00:05:42.604 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>Go! Get out!</i>

00:05:45.773 --> 00:05:46.641 position:66% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:05:47.442 --> 00:05:48.276 position:5% line:5% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>This is not normal...</i>

00:05:49.211 --> 00:05:50.779 position:5% line:83% align:start
This is really what we came here
 to see?!

00:05:51.780 --> 00:05:54.483 position:27% line:83% align:start
If the findings from our
research are correct...

00:05:54.716 --> 00:05:58.387 position:7% line:83% align:start
...what isn't normal in here is
Akari Hizamaru.

00:06:03.627 --> 00:06:05.295 position:5% line:89% align:start
(YURIKO) <i>Um, Akari?</i>

00:06:05.928 --> 00:06:08.899 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>About last week, Sorry I was so</i>
 <i>mean.</i>

00:06:08.932 --> 00:06:10.801 position:7% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>It's probably for the</i>
 <i>better, anyway.</i>

00:06:11.301 --> 00:06:12.302 position:5% line:89% align:start
(YURIKO) <i>huh?</i>

00:06:14.672 --> 00:06:18.509 position:5% line:71% align:start
(AKARI) <i>I mean, once you get to</i>
 <i>college, carrying a little</i>
 <i>doll around with you isn't going</i>
 <i>to be too cool! </i>

00:06:19.944 --> 00:06:21.145 position:35% line:89% align:start
 [chuckle]

00:06:23.214 --> 00:06:24.782 position:21% line:89% align:start
We did it, you know.

00:06:25.316 --> 00:06:26.352 position:24% line:89% align:start
 <i>We found a donor.</i>

00:06:26.385 --> 00:06:28.587 position:27% line:89% align:start
[gasp] Really?!

00:06:29.355 --> 00:06:33.826 position:5% line:77% align:start
(AKARI) <i>It's real alright. I've</i>
 <i>got one more thing I need to</i>
 <i>take care of.</i>

00:06:36.262 --> 00:06:37.863 position:16% line:89% align:start
Just imagine it, Yuriko!

00:06:38.498 --> 00:06:41.334 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>You're almost there! What are</i>
 <i>you going to do</i>
 <i>first?</i>

00:06:41.968 --> 00:06:44.504 position:27% line:89% align:start
Uh?... [chuckle]

00:06:45.272 --> 00:06:46.440 position:24% line:89% align:start
Go eat some ramen?

00:06:46.674 --> 00:06:48.509 position:10% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) <i>You got it! And then</i>
 <i>what?</i>

00:06:49.976 --> 00:06:51.212 position:27% line:89% align:start
Go snowboarding!

00:06:52.280 --> 00:06:53.180 position:5% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) [chuckle] <i>Yeah that'll </i>
 <i>be great!</i>

00:06:53.614 --> 00:06:54.815 position:21% line:89% align:start
And have some beer!

00:06:54.849 --> 00:06:56.518 position:5% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Sure, just not too much!</i>

00:06:57.352 --> 00:06:58.487 position:21% line:89% align:start
And then Space Land!

00:06:59.588 --> 00:07:00.855 position:7% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) [chuckle] <i>It'll be a </i>
 <i>ghost town!</i>

00:07:01.990 --> 00:07:04.960 position:10% line:83% align:start
And then... and then... and
then...

00:07:11.567 --> 00:07:13.536 position:21% line:89% align:start
[holding back tears]

00:07:13.870 --> 00:07:18.207 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>But why, Akari? Why are you so </i>
 <i>good to me?</i>

00:07:21.378 --> 00:07:22.713 position:13% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>Why wouldn't I be?</i>

00:07:23.981 --> 00:07:28.720 position:7% line:83% align:start
 <i>I... Your kindness, it changed</i>
 <i>me... Ever since that day.</i>

00:07:29.019 --> 00:07:35.560 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>I lo- Uh... You... you just mean</i>
 <i>so much to me.</i>

00:07:39.030 --> 00:07:40.733 position:19% line:89% align:start
 <i>You're my best friend.</i>

00:07:42.301 --> 00:07:44.770 position:21% line:89% align:start
[labored breathing]

00:07:45.438 --> 00:07:45.938 position:38% line:89% align:start
[growl]

00:07:55.048 --> 00:07:56.516 position:50% line:89% align:start
 Huh?! He's up?!

00:07:57.685 --> 00:07:59.654 position:35% line:89% align:start
[snarling]

00:07:59.687 --> 00:08:01.922 position:33% line:89% align:start
 [growling]

00:08:02.623 --> 00:08:04.625 position:44% line:89% align:start
[intense snarling]

00:08:04.659 --> 00:08:05.693 position:35% line:89% align:start
[growling]

00:08:06.427 --> 00:08:07.562 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:08:11.065 --> 00:08:12.368 position:24% line:89% align:start
[growling in pain]

00:08:12.401 --> 00:08:13.669 position:24% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) [yelling]

00:08:13.702 --> 00:08:15.270 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:08:15.604 --> 00:08:16.872 position:24% line:89% align:start
(EMCEE) It's a take down!

00:08:17.606 --> 00:08:18.608 position:33% line:89% align:start
 <i>But what-?!</i>

00:08:19.776 --> 00:08:21.778 position:38% line:89% align:start
 [Thud]

00:08:27.785 --> 00:08:29.787 position:19% line:89% align:start
(EMCEE) [gasp] <i>My God.</i>

00:08:30.453 --> 00:08:32.790 position:21% line:89% align:start
 <i>Di-did he just.</i> ..?!

00:08:37.094 --> 00:08:43.968 position:10% line:77% align:start
 <i>I don't believe it. A-Akari </i>
 <i>Hizamaru has won! He's actually</i>
 <i>won!</i>

00:08:44.636 --> 00:08:48.974 position:10% line:77% align:start
(SHOKICHI) So, another does
exist. Another child born after
the procedure.

00:08:50.475 --> 00:08:51.878 position:21% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>What? What?!</i>

00:08:51.910 --> 00:08:52.812 position:24% line:89% align:start
 [thud and groan]

00:08:53.813 --> 00:08:55.981 position:5% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) You promised! You gave
me your word!

00:08:56.416 --> 00:08:58.618 position:5% line:83% align:start
N-No. Stop! [grunts and
struggling]

00:08:58.651 --> 00:09:00.821 position:7% line:83% align:start
Give her the surgery! And save
her!

00:09:01.421 --> 00:09:03.089 position:5% line:89% align:start
(BOOKIE) [struggling to breath]

00:09:03.424 --> 00:09:05.057 position:30% line:89% align:start
We sold her...

00:09:05.091 --> 00:09:06.627 position:35% line:89% align:start
The girl.

00:09:06.660 --> 00:09:08.829 position:52% line:89% align:start
What?! To who?!

00:09:09.496 --> 00:09:10.597 position:16% line:89% align:start
 [struggling to breathe]

00:09:12.132 --> 00:09:16.538 position:5% line:83% align:start
(BOOKIE) [coughing, trying to
breathe]

00:09:16.571 --> 00:09:20.675 position:16% line:83% align:start
(AKARI) [angered heavy
breathing]

00:09:20.709 --> 00:09:21.844 position:5% line:89% align:start
You bastard!

00:09:22.444 --> 00:09:23.913 position:38% line:89% align:start
Bring her back <i>now</i> !

00:09:24.145 --> 00:09:25.113 position:33% line:89% align:start
She's dead.

00:09:26.615 --> 00:09:29.151 position:10% line:83% align:start
We did what we could, but two
days ago...

00:09:29.185 --> 00:09:30.352 position:5% line:89% align:start
 [gasp]

00:09:37.861 --> 00:09:42.834 position:5% line:89% align:start
No... It's a lie. You're lying!

00:09:48.706 --> 00:09:49.707 position:13% line:89% align:start
(MICHELLE) <i>These people...</i>

00:09:51.409 --> 00:09:54.111 position:5% line:77% align:start
They never had any intention of
finding your friend a donor.
They're the bastards.

00:09:54.713 --> 00:09:56.548 position:5% line:83% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>By the time we found</i>
 <i>her...</i>

00:09:57.048 --> 00:10:01.520 position:5% line:83% align:start
 <i>...it was too late. I'm sorry we</i>
 <i>didn't make it in time.</i>

00:10:01.553 --> 00:10:06.893 position:16% line:89% align:start
No... no... Give her back...

00:10:07.527 --> 00:10:09.562 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sobbing] Please.

00:10:15.068 --> 00:10:16.737 position:30% line:89% align:start
 <i>Give her back!</i>

00:10:26.046 --> 00:10:27.047 position:5% line:89% align:start
[sniffling]

00:10:28.048 --> 00:10:29.049 position:69% line:89% align:start
 Akari...

00:10:30.151 --> 00:10:32.654 position:10% line:83% align:start
Lots of kids out there like
Yuriko need your help

00:10:33.054 --> 00:10:35.156 position:5% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:10:36.959 --> 00:10:39.962 position:5% line:89% align:start
 I'm Shokichi Komachi.

00:10:40.563 --> 00:10:42.765 position:7% line:83% align:start
I command the Mars Exploration
Team...

00:10:43.766 --> 00:10:46.670 position:5% line:83% align:start
...from the U.N.'s Aeronautics
and Space Administration.

00:10:46.870 --> 00:10:48.070 position:33% line:89% align:start
Or "U-NASA."

00:10:48.772 --> 00:10:49.606 position:35% line:89% align:start
 <i>And I'm...</i>

00:10:50.474 --> 00:10:51.775 position:7% line:83% align:start
Michelle K. Davis, second in
command.

00:10:52.242 --> 00:10:53.610 position:27% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) <i>U-NASA?</i>

00:10:53.945 --> 00:10:55.212 position:21% line:89% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>Correct. </i>

00:10:56.948 --> 00:10:59.116 position:7% line:77% align:start
 <i>The disease that cut Yuriko's</i>
 <i>life short is no ordinary</i>
 <i>sickness. </i>

00:10:59.551 --> 00:11:01.986 position:13% line:83% align:start
 <i>It's a virus that did not</i>
 <i>originate on Earth.</i>

00:11:02.020 --> 00:11:03.721 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sigh]

00:11:05.123 --> 00:11:09.628 position:5% line:77% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>And it will continue </i>
 <i>to spread. As a result, many</i>
 <i>will die.</i>

00:11:10.796 --> 00:11:15.969 position:5% line:77% align:start
 <i>To stop the virus, we must fly </i>
 <i>to Mars. We have two years to</i>
 <i>prepare. </i>

00:11:16.803 --> 00:11:17.704 position:64% line:89% align:start
To Mars...?

00:11:19.071 --> 00:11:21.841 position:5% line:77% align:start
We need you as a part of our
elite unit. We need
your strength.

00:11:22.976 --> 00:11:25.579 position:5% line:83% align:start
And we need your rage as well,
Akari.

00:11:26.146 --> 00:11:29.650 position:5% line:83% align:start
I, too, lost someone dear to me.
On Mars.

00:11:31.586 --> 00:11:33.721 position:41% line:89% align:start
(AKARI) [quivering]

00:11:33.754 --> 00:11:37.491 position:10% line:77% align:start
(SHOKICHI) <i>I'm not like the </i>
